@NODE "SysReq" "System Requirements"




                            System Requirements
                           ********************

  Amiga WorkBench 3.0 and Kickstart 3.0 or Greater.
 
  At least 4 meg Ram.

  5 meg hard drive space. 

  Mui 3.7 or Greater Installed.
  
  ClassAct Installed.

  Info needed from Sevice Provider with a POP3 mail system

  Login name

  Login password

                Username (May be the same as your Login name).





