@NODE "History" "History"




                                 History
                                *********

  
Version 1.5

Version 1 must be installed before using the upgrade.
A much better Control Gui programmed with ClassAct.
Added Connect and Dis-connect for Miami to the Gui.
Added AmTelnet and AmFTP.
History listview to kept a check on what you have done.

Version 1.6

No longer need to have version 1 installed first.
Put all programs together in 1 install script.
Added a new install package that can be used for Demon accounts.
You can now use any version of Miami.

Version 1.7

You can use generic version of Miami, AmFTP, & AmTelnet.
Links changed to the newest version on Aminet.

Version 2.0

If you already have Yam, Voyager, AmFTP, AmTelnet, Miami
installed on your system you will be asked if you would
like these copied over instead of reinstalling them.

Version 2.1

Changed over from using Voyager to IBrowse.
Also changed AmFTP over to DaFTP.
Different SendMail Program now uses Yam.

(You must check that the Mailto adress is right ie.

steve@cliffe.demon.co.uk Is Ok.

Steven Chapman <steve@cliffe.demon.co.uk> Is Not.

Version 2.2 (Changed Gui Only)

Enforcer hit fixed.
Getnews now run's as a background task.

Version 2.3 & 2.4

My testing Only

New For Version 2.5

Done away with the 4 external scripts for Miami.
Mailkick no longer needed. 
Different SendMail Program now uses Yam.
(You must check that the Mailto adress is right ie.
steve@cliffe.demon.co.uk Is Ok.
Steven Chapman <steve@cliffe.demon.co.uk> Is Not.)
Different postnews program used.
SendNews now incorporated into NetFace's Gui.
No longer need's two install script's. 
(Common and Demon user's now use the same script.).


