@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"




                               Introduction
                              **************


              NetFace is complete Internet Package Providing 
                 Mail, News, Ftp, Telnet & Web browsing.

           The NetFace Package is a collection of files mostly 
            from Aminet, With an install script to un-arc and 
             install these onto your hard drive complete with 
                       an easy to use frontend GUI.

            The Installer will make a drawer called 'NetFace' 
                where you specify and in it, it will place 

                         Miami as the TCP/IP stack
                      GRn as the offline Newsreader.
                     NewsAgent1.4 as the News Browser.
                    Geditor as the News & Mail editor.
                        IBrowse as the Web Browser.
                          YAM as the Mail Client.
                         DaFTP as the FTP Client.
                         AmTelnet as the Telnet Client.

               WBRun this is used just to launch NewsAgent.
                     CDRun is used to run IBrowse.

             And several extra files in the bin directory ie.
                              Postnews, ect.  
       It will also copy some fonts (GRn.font) to your fonts drawer.
             and two libraries to Libs: and three files to C:

                This version of NetFace allows the user to

                      Connect / Dis-Connect Miami.

                   Run NNTPTransfer the Get News Button.

    The SendNews Button will post any news items that you have written.

                 The Web Browser Button launches IBrowse.

                       The Mail Button launches Yam.
                       
                   The AmTelnet Button launches AmTelnet.
                       
             The DaFTP Button, yes you guessed it, launches DaFTP.

       The News Browser Button Launches NewsAgent but this will only
                         run when you are Online.

  And the News Reader Button runs a script (PrepNews) that unbatches the 
    files created by NNTPTransfer and NewsAgent (NewsBatch or NABatch) 
                    and then load your newsreader GRn.






                       @{"        Back To Main          " Link "Main"}          


@ENDNODE

@NODE "Usage" "Usage"




                     How To Use This Internet Package.
                   ************************************

   
   a/ Run the program Netface that is located in the NetFace drawer
      (this program can be placed anywhere on your hard drive).

      Switch on your modem and click on the Connect button.
      And wait for Miami to connect you to your Internet server.

   b/ To collect/send mail click on the Yam button.
      This will then launch the mail program. (Read Yam docs for more info)

   c/ The Browse button launches the News Browser.(NewsAgent)
      This program only works while you are online, And lists just the
      subject  lines of the choosen newsgroup, Click on the items of 
      interest and it will just download these.  (Read NewsAgent docs for
      more info)

   d/ The Get All button launches a script that downloads all the items in
      the newsgroups listed in the File called NewsGroups that can be found
      in NetFace/Usr/Lib/.

   e/ The News Reader button launches another script that unbatches the news
      items that the above two program downloads, And than runs the 
      NewsReader  program.

   f/ SendNews button.  After writing or replying to a news item, when 
      next online, click on this button to send these items off.

  




